'''Michael Maguire''' is a Northern Irish public servant and former [[management consultant]]. Since July 2012, he has served as the [[Police Ombudsman for Northern Ireland]]. He was previously the Chief Inspector of the Criminal Justice Inspectorate in Northern Ireland (2008 to 2012). Before moving into public service, he worked as a management consultant with [[PA Consulting Group]] and was a Director of [[Price Waterhouse]].<ref name="bio Omb">{{cite web|title=Dr Michael Maguire: The Police Ombudsman|url=https://policeombudsman.org/About-Us/Staff-Profiles/Dr-Michael-Maguire|website=Police Ombudsman for Northern Ireland|accessdate=19 October 2017}}</ref><ref name="to be">{{cite web|title=Maguire to be Police Ombudsman|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-northern-ireland-17616976|website=BBC News|accessdate=19 October 2017|date=4 April 2012}}</ref><ref name="New BT">{{cite news|title=New police ombudsman appointed|url=http://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/news/northern-ireland/new-police-ombudsman-appointed-28734801.html|accessdate=19 October 2017|work=Belfast Telegraph|date=4 April 2012}}</ref>

